headline: The Magnificent Seven Drove Markets. Now They’re Pulling in Different Directions.
summary: The Magnificent Seven is now the Mag Five.  Investors are no longer grouping the market’s big tech stocks together in quite the same way.  The fortunes of what was once Wall Street’s favorite band of megacap names have diverged in the past year, as professional and ordinary investors alike take a more cautious view of the artificial-intelligence spending boom.
